[h3 id=Tricksandglitches 
	" Tricks and glitches
	$LF
]h3
[h4 id=Cornerboosting 
	" Corner boosting
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Touching a corner diagonally can push Link forward a little, 
	$LF
	"and saves 1 or 2 frames per boost.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Up/Down+Item 
	" Up/Down + Item
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Each item use causes glitches by pressing up and down at the same time.
	$LF
	"Since it allows Link to touch sprites in the remote position, 
	$LF
	"he can retrieve his sword without moving below.
	$LF
	"Want to see the annoying owl? I guess you don't ;)
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"In the last battle, he becomes invisible by side effect.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=Doghousewarpglitch 
	" Doghouse warp glitch
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"As you can imagine, the warp is the heart of the run.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"When approaching the entrance of the doghouse downwards along its right side, 
	$LF
	"you can touch the entrance by pushing left, and it takes Link to a random room.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"The destination depends on the number of enemies you killed.
	$LF
	"Also, it becomes zero when restarting the game.
	$LF
	"In the run, Link goes out from the village and kills two enemies after he steals a bow.
	$LF
	"This might look redundant, but is necessary to access the proper room.
	$LF
]div
[h3 id=Tacticsaboutthebossbattle 
	" Tactics about the boss battle
	$LF
]h3
[h4 id=1stform 
	" 1st form
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Normally, the boss cannot be hurt without magic powder, 
	$LF
	"however, you can defeat him by slashing simultaneously with his landing.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=2ndform 
	" 2nd form
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Actually, Deluxe Shovel has an ability to reflect beam.
	$LF
	"Shovel use in this scene was done just for an entertainment.
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=3rdform 
	" 3rd form
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Normally, Link needs to slash again after a hit to focus the power into his sword.
	$LF
	"But you can cancel the motion of swinging a sword with Deluxe Shovel,
	$LF
	"then save 16 frames per once.
	$LF
]div
[div class=p 
	"This is the exact use of Deluxe Shovel™, eh? ;)
	$LF
]div
[h4 id=6thform 
	" 6th form
	$LF
]h4
[div class=p 
	"Don't be too close to the boss, if you want five hits or more.
	$LF
	"You can in fact get six hits by shooting arrows while you approach to the boss from far.
	$LF
]div
